487
00:30:33,913 --> 00:30:36,416
...and two kids in Greece and hoped
to bring them to this country.

488
00:30:37,083 --> 00:30:39,252
We didn't pay attention to
the long hours he worked.

489
00:30:39,627 --> 00:30:43,339
We didn't see any of that.
