501
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:22,295
Michael Sullivan.

502
00:31:22,962 --> 00:31:24,756
The Court hereby sentences
you to be remanded...

503
00:31:24,797 --> 00:31:26,508
...for a period of no more than
18 months...

504
00:31:26,716 --> 00:31:28,968
...no less than 1 year at
the Wilkinson Home for Boys.

505
00:31:29,761 --> 00:31:31,971
And I might add...
had it not been for the intervention...

506
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:35,225
...of Father Robert Carrillo who spoke
